0-13T15:16:41.000Z","msg":"聽講防暴仲多過手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:46:04.000Z","msg":"黃大仙先慘，一開始二點半狗到，set防線，二點九推，之後用車追，成個過程唔夠 10分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連被捕。<br />\n<br />\n另外，手足瘋跑，有人慢行散步、行下停下，最後累到一兩手足咩都無搞過就被捕！<br />\n<br />\n之後！大隊逃亡到鑽石山，荷里活 勁旺勁熱鬧勁多人，平行時空咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，同埋賓賓啲人重多過我哋手足，大家比人防暴追一次之後就返晒屋企，散晒，再聚唔返！！<br />\n<br />\n今日黃大仙今雖然唔係做得咁好！甚至可以話係做差！但係我哋不指責！更應該從中吸取教訓，下次做好啲。<br />\n<br />\n今日二點尼到，完全無街坊、和理非、哨兵、單車兵、物資兵等，大家都唔見咗人，可能見十八區太散，有手足跨咗區，變相就扔底咗我哋呢道唔夠 100人係道，經過今日呢個教訓，有手足被捕！我希望大家！下次可以改善下，做好啲！"},{"pid":"980e5014fcee95c045b0ec962d71e92c6f63d35f","tid":1652191,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"585e7f64f01b21574afe9a422ed73a24a7a6b31b","tid":1652191,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:44:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:46:05.000Z","msg":"澳門狗又說三道四"},{"pid":"c72d5fe7dc30650e5e102fd3b1ec5bb61a466cc3","tid":1652191,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5bc03107f8244148552bbd5ab9364a9a6f6c3c2","tid":1652191,"uid":250356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"058bcf5df6b5d344cfdddf61c21780ed523f8bf2","tid":1652191,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1877d948dede9277000baaae0996b160a58f31c6","tid":1652191,"uid":206440,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:14:15.000Z","msg":"六至七區啦<br />\n今日港島真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完全唔知做乜鳩嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:16:41.000Z","msg":"聽講防暴仲多過手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-1